train_3 = train_2 %>%
  mutate(nightwork = ifelse(hour(date) == 18 & Light > 400, 1, 0))

test_3 = test_2 %>%
  mutate(nightwork = ifelse(hour(date) == 18 & Light > 400, 1, 0))
